#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn8.9"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn8.9:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 8 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 8 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn8.9:0.2"
msgid "1. Vaṅgīsavagga "
msgstr "1. With Vaṅgīsa "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn8.9:0.3"
msgid "9. Koṇḍaññasutta "
msgstr "9. With Koṇḍañña "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts1ed1.194, pts2ed1.418, sc1
msgctxt "sn8.9:1.1"
msgid "Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā rājagahe viharati veḷuvane kalandakanivāpe. "
msgstr "At one time the Buddha was staying near Rājagaha, in the Bamboo Grove, the squirrels’ feeding ground. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. VAR: aññāsikoṇḍañño → aññākoṇḍañño (bj, s1-3, km, pts2)
msgctxt "sn8.9:1.2"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmā aññāsikoṇḍañño sucirasseva yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavato pādesu sirasā nipatitvā bhagavato pādāni mukhena ca paricumbati, pāṇīhi ca parisambāhati, nāmañca sāveti: "
msgstr "Then Venerable Koṇḍañña Who Understood approached the Buddha after a very long absence. He bowed with his head to the Buddha’s feet, caressing them and covering them with kisses, and pronounced his name: "

msgctxt "sn8.9:1.3"
msgid "“koṇḍaññohaṃ, bhagavā, koṇḍaññohaṃ, sugatā”ti. "
msgstr "“I am Koṇḍañña, Blessed One! I am Koṇḍañña, Holy One!” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn8.9:1.4"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmato vaṅgīsassa etadahosi: "
msgstr "Then Venerable Vaṅgīsa thought, "

msgctxt "sn8.9:1.5"
msgid "“ayaṃ kho āyasmā aññāsikoṇḍañño sucirasseva yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavato pādesu sirasā nipatitvā bhagavato pādāni mukhena ca paricumbati, pāṇīhi ca parisambāhati, nāmañca sāveti: "
msgstr "“This Venerable Koṇḍañña Who Understood has approached the Buddha after a very long absence. He bowed with his head to the Buddha’s feet, caressing them and covering them with kisses, and pronounced his name: "

msgctxt "sn8.9:1.6"
msgid "‘koṇḍaññohaṃ, bhagavā, koṇḍaññohaṃ, sugatā’ti. "
msgstr "‘I am Koṇḍañña, Blessed One! I am Koṇḍañña, Holy One!’ "

msgctxt "sn8.9:1.7"
msgid "Yannūnāhaṃ āyasmantaṃ aññāsikoṇḍaññaṃ bhagavato sammukhā sāruppāhi gāthāhi abhitthaveyyan”ti. "
msgstr "Why don’t I extoll him in the Buddha’s presence with fitting verses?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn8.9:2.1"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmā vaṅgīso uṭṭhāyāsanā ekaṃsaṃ uttarāsaṅgaṃ karitvā yena bhagavā tenañjaliṃ paṇāmetvā bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "Then Venerable Vaṅgīsa got up from his seat, arranged his robe over one shoulder, raised his joined palms toward the Buddha, and said, "

msgctxt "sn8.9:2.2"
msgid "“paṭibhāti maṃ, bhagavā, paṭibhāti maṃ, sugatā”ti. "
msgstr "“I feel inspired to speak, Blessed One! I feel inspired to speak, Holy One!” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn8.9:2.3"
msgid "“Paṭibhātu taṃ, vaṅgīsā”ti bhagavā avoca. "
msgstr "“Then speak as you feel inspired,” said the Buddha. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn8.9:2.4"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmā vaṅgīso āyasmantaṃ aññāsikoṇḍaññaṃ bhagavato sammukhā sāruppāhi gāthāhi abhitthavi: "
msgstr "Then Vaṅgīsa extolled Koṇḍañña in the Buddha’s presence with fitting verses: "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn8.9:3.1"
msgid "“Buddhānubuddho so thero, "
msgstr "“The senior monk who was awakened right after the Buddha, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn8.9:3.2"
msgid "koṇḍañño tibbanikkamo; "
msgstr "Koṇḍañña, is keenly energetic. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn8.9:3.3"
msgid "Lābhī sukhavihārānaṃ, "
msgstr "He regularly gains blissful meditative states, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn8.9:3.4"
msgid "vivekānaṃ abhiṇhaso. "
msgstr "and the three kinds of seclusion. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts2ed1.419, sc4
msgctxt "sn8.9:4.1"
msgid "Yaṃ sāvakena pattabbaṃ, "
msgstr "Whatever can be attained by a disciple "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn8.9:4.2"
msgid "satthusāsanakārinā; "
msgstr "who does the Teacher’s bidding, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn8.9:4.3"
msgid "Sabbassa taṃ anuppattaṃ, "
msgstr "he has attained it all, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn8.9:4.4"
msgid "appamattassa sikkhato. "
msgstr "through diligently training himself. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "sn8.9:5.1"
msgid "Mahānubhāvo tevijjo, "
msgstr "With great power and the three knowledges, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn8.9:5.2"
msgid "cetopariyāyakovido; "
msgstr "expert in comprehending the minds of others, "

#. HTML: <br>
#. VAR: buddhadāyādo → buddhasāvako (pts1)
msgctxt "sn8.9:5.3"
msgid "Koṇḍañño buddhadāyādo, "
msgstr "Koṇḍañña, the heir to the Buddha, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn8.9:5.4"
msgid "pāde vandati satthuno”ti. "
msgstr "bows at the Teacher’s feet.”"

#. HTML: </p></blockquote></article></section></body></html>
